snippet.title: Galaxy on Fire 3 (CGI Launch Trailer)
snippet.description:
The official CGI launch trailer of Galaxy on Fire 3, out now on the App Store for free! Get it NOW and show your piloting skills in explosive dogfights on the outskirts of space!

The pioneering sci-fi shooter on mobile returns with Galaxy on Fire 3. Take course for the far-off Neox Sector and take down the galaxy's most wanted criminals and their devoted legions of underlings.
